778
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:05,920
Gambar sampul Moments.

779
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:07,520
Jadi ini tentang Shi Min.

780
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:10,000
Saya tidak yakin,

781
00:39:10,360 --> 00:39:11,720
