798
00:39:39,720 --> 00:39:40,520
Hai, Shi Min.

799
00:39:40,960 --> 00:39:42,200
Apakah Anda sudah menghubungi Big G?

800
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,680
Dia sedang bersamaku sekarang.

801
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:50,040
Mohon segera kirimkan lokasi Anda.

802
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:51,520
Ibu Big G sangat panik.

803
