821
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:47,680
Dia ada di sana?

822
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:49,040
Saya mendengar orang-orang berbicara di teleponnya.

823
00:40:49,080 --> 00:40:49,760
Mereka menyebutkan

824
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:52,000
